::KitKat::

She saw the spotted bot moving around.  She heard "here kity" from the large 
bug bot.  She saw the othe male getting ready for attack.  the Female wasn't 
doing to much.  She was tired of the cat and mouse games so she decided to 
reveil herself.  She stood up on the bluff and she howled.  She ran down the 
hill and charged at the spotted bot(Cheetor)  She leaped and jumped over him 
and stood only a few yards away and bared her teeth and growled at him 
fieresly.
"Back you pile of kitty litter.  BACK!"
She advanced a few feet and kept growling and showing her teeth in true 
canine fasion.
"Pathetic Maximal. You don't even stand up and fight when challenged. 
Fight!"

Her Predacon symbol showed proudly on her shoulder.
"Maximals are week for they don't ever fight.  FIGHT!"
